knowledgeGraph.title: Park City Hospital
knowledgeGraph.description: Park City Hospital is a full-service community hospital in Park City, Utah, United States. It is located at 900 Round Valley Drive at the northwest corner of Keetley Junction US-40/US-189 and SR-248. It a service of Intermountain Healthcare, a nonprofit health care system serving the Intermountain West.
